      <title>Rob McEwen 寻求 1 亿美元收购阿根廷铜矿，Milei 提振前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/mcewen-seeks-100-million-for-argentina-copper-mine-as-milei-boosts-prospects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大企业家 Rob McEwen 正在洽谈为阿根廷的一个铜矿项目筹集约 1 亿美元的资金，而此时矿商们押注哈维尔·米雷 (Javier Milei) 新政府放松管制将提振该行业的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/mcewen-seeks-100-million-for-argentina-copper-mine-as-milei-boosts-prospects</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 17:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
